{"tid":2486769,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲前國防部長：印太地區軍事衝突一觸即發","createTime":"2021-04-13T06:05:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T08:42:55.000Z","uid":124021,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8b6690d11f1de368aca68fc5ca8935c204738ecc","tid":2486769,"uid":124021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T06:05:16.000Z","msg":"澳洲前國防部長貝恩（Christopher Pyne）星期一（4 月 12 日）於阿德雷德大學發表演說，<strong><span class=\"red\">警告指印太地區爆發牽涉中國的戰爭的機會正在急劇上升，又指台灣問題將是戰爭觸發點。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n他在出席大學畢業禮時發表演說，指「中國的戰略姿態已不如以前一樣溫和」，令美國及其他盟友感到不安。他說：「現實是中國有信心、有能力，亦不會隱藏（這一點）。」<br />\n<br />\n他強調<strong><span class=\"red\">，所指的並非單純「網絡戰爭」，「而是一場涉及人命損傷、軍事設施遭破壞的動能戰爭」。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「這並非修辭誇大。這是你和我未來五到十年期間可能需要面對的事情。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n貝恩又表示，目前印度太平洋地區發生「軍事動能戰爭」的可能性，較他開始擔任國防工業部長時高得多。他說：「五年前，我曾說過這（爆發戰爭）的可能性極細。現在我不得不說，這個可能性較當時更大。」"},{"pid":"5c279158912bfe52b7214003bd4dba8d9a6d40b1","tid":2486769,"uid":258345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T06:07:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想死呀"},{"pid":"6ad281e3316ceebdcb053e533aa9476ca75969b2","tid":2486769,"uid":155095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T06:08:12.000Z","msg":"第三次世界大戰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/DeepNegligibleCarpenterant-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FDeepNegligibleCarpenterant-size_restricted.gif&h=17ea81c0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"42f636774bda383bf6ff97c167fd9d8095ac559d","tid":2486769,"uid":199456,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T06:09:00.